"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"On January 18, Microsoft issued a statement saying that it will acquire Activision Blizzard at a price of $95 per share, in an all-cash transaction valued at $68.7 billion. The Microsoft CEO referred to the Metaverse several times in his statement, saying: \\\"Games are the most dynamic and exciting entertainment category on any platform today, and will play a key role in the development of the Metaverse platform. We are making an impact on the world. Deep investment in best-in-class content, community and cloud to usher in a new era of gaming that puts players and creators first, and makes games safe, inclusive and accessible to all.‚Äù\",\"timestamp\":1642733275,\"title\":\"Microsoft CEO: Games will play a key role in the development of the Metaverse platform\"},\"digest\":\"VZDirPJaXX7iDa6YxPfaiOZPNLhTRxyxAcQZfPqzxIU\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xC650D8B1cdA8bfDA725CfC8b3E40d956e9ABcaC1\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"CCzOHFv8OKXBzxsefUMR1Ect9nWMQOha8j_dnuhoqyY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"McnzZBJRSu23oOf7yg0K5lbJ7VoSJ7K75Fm91hBUTRo\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"BJiQFiVdg0hWfv6q0cDSn-sc1qDay0q1eFzGzRaALKT-oP-rIiC1jULtp8820P_386lrvhWopi8UAHxw5XgQ4w\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0x43451a5228d417b2a789f88b0ccaee53070d10d03a114c1ce330111af37b96dc774b5eb23d7a29b918fdabef4f3c2a3acda0e885ab1cd2f33d78f2191b64c5911b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"CCzOHFv8OKXBzxsefUMR1Ect9nWMQOha8j_dnuhoqyY\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"McnzZBJRSu23oOf7yg0K5lbJ7VoSJ7K75Fm91hBUTRo\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"VZDirPJaXX7iDa6YxPfaiOZPNLhTRxyxAcQZfPqzxIU\"}"